content: Hi John! Thanks for checking in. Please post this in one of your Persuasion channels so those folks can help you.
Thank you - I am set over there...I thought there were other text teams besides the Persuasion Text group..
There are, but we are done with trainings this close to the election; we are recommending people join Persuasion or check <#1268426751164551199> channel. Thanks for being here!
I participated in the text training, passed a test...but didn't get an invite. If I missed something, or there is no need, I am fine.
Let me send you a DM.
I took text training with NV dems today and I'm doing text banking with them.  Please let me know if there is other training I can take or if there are other text banks I can help with.
Thanks for following up in the DM's!

Our text trainings have ended, but you can check out ⁠⁠the <#1268426751164551199> or <#1298623273566732300> channels. We would also love help with making phone calls during this final stretch -- you can sign up for that at https://events.democrats.org/event/725393/ . Thank you!
Now that I took training and have been added to text bank,  how do I get started tomorrow on campaigns? Do I look at "<#1265788349747171438> around 11AM/12PM ET to select one to work on?

Hi <@1298054117909991455> Please see the DM regarding getting texts, but you are correct that you will need to go to TextingCampaigns channel and click on the reply links there. Thanks so much! <:thankyou:1252806147396735057>
